description:
This #DevCraftKE panel focused on the expert beginner. Expert Beginners are developers who do not understand enough of the big picture to understand that they aren’t actually experts. Panelists talked about their early days as developers and had some great advice for up and coming developers.

Moderator: Leonard Korir - Cofounder & CEO, Mobidev Solutions
Sheilah Birgen, Head of Community Services, iHub
Marie Githinji- Co-founder and CTO, eLimu
Caine Wanjau - CTO, Twiga Foods
Kago Kagichiri - Co-founder & CEO, Eneza Education
